t-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">كالبول، والغائط، والدم المسفوح.</span></p>','<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-3f1840f0-7fff-3aaf-2539-adb4c709b53f\"></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\">\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">قال تعالى: ﴿</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #40ad48; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> قُلْ لَا أَجِدُ فِي مَا أُوحِيَ إِلَيَّ مُحَرَّمًا عَلَى طَاعِمٍ يَطْعَمُهُ إِلَّا أَنْ يَكُونَ مَيْتَةً أَوْ دَمًا مَسْفُوحًا أَوْ لَحْمَ خِنْزِيرٍ فَإِنَّهُ رِجْسٌ</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> ﴾ [الأنعام: 145].</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">قال تعالى: ﴿ </span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #40ad48; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">وَيُنَزِّلُ عَلَيْكُمْ مِنَ السَّمَاءِ مَاءً لِيُطَهِّرَكُمْ بِه ِ</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">﴾ [الأنفال: 11].</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">عن أنس بن مالك: أن أعرابياً بال في المسجد، فقاموا إليه، فقال رسول الله [: &laquo;لا تُزْرِموهُ&raquo; ثم دعا بدلو من ماء فصب عليه&raquo; رواه البخاري.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditiona