oration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">س/ لماذا نتوضأ؟ وبماذا نتوضأ؟</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; background-color: #e2efd9; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ج/&nbsp; حين نريد: الصلاةَ أو الطوافَ أو مسَّ المصحف،&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; background-color: #e2efd9; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">فإنا نتوضأ بالماء الطهور.</span></p>\r\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-556b4184-7fff-cf11-46ff-71b5012b7c58\"></span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; background-color: #e2efd9; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #ff0000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">وأما الماء الذي وقعت فيه نجاسة؛ فغيّرت لونَه&nbsp; أو طعمَه أو ريحه: فهو نجس</span></p>','<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-70b331e7-7fff-f4b1-74c3-0f1d2c4d4f38\"></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\">\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list