pre-wrap;\">س١/</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #9f8f8a; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">وضح الماء الطهور؟</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #c07748; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">س٢/</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #9f8f8a; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">متى يتنجس الماء؟</span></p>\r\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-a0be4cf1-7fff-2a80-a579-36ad7ca30002\"></span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">س3/ أحضر مع زملائك ما تيسرَّ من المياه والسوائل كماء من بئر، أو فيه طين، أو ملح، أو صابون، ثم بيِّن: ما الذي ي