ttom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">س٢/ متى تقصر الصلاة في السفر؟ ومتى تسقط عنه؟</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">س/ مثل بصفة عملية صلاة المريض الجالس، أو الذي لا يستطيع الحركة إلَّا بعينيه</span></p>\r\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-90128bf1-7fff-635b-f1c9-1026cd560c2f\"></span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>',NULL,49,3,NULL,NULL,'2022-01-13 09:56:00','2022-09-01 11:29:09'),(54,'صلاةُ الجماعة وأحْكام المسجِد:','صلاة الجماعة وأحكام المسجد','<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\">\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; background-color: #e2efd9; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">س/ ما المقصود بصلاة الجماعة؟ وماذا يلزَمُنا في المسجِد؟</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; background-color: #e2efd9; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ج/ على الرجال: الاجتماع لأداء الصلوات الخمس المفروضة،&nbsp; -إلا لعذر-.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; background-color: #e2efd9; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">وتُصلى الجماعةُ في المساجد إن أمكن.</span></p>\r\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-d1ae3fbe-7fff-f9b1-6713-36fb75eb55ef\"></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\">\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; background-color: #e2efd9; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">وإذا دخل المسجد فعليه:</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\">\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -54pt;\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; background-color: #e2efd9; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">أن يحترم المسجد،</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -54pt;\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; background-color: #e2efd9; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ولا يؤذي المصلين بريح أو غيره.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>','<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-7220b3fa-7fff-2951-c632-d5d3d7f712aa\"></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\">\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">قال تعالى: ﴿ </span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #40ad48; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">فِي بُيُوتٍ أَذِنَ اللَّهُ أَنْ تُرْفَعَ وَيُذْكَرَ فِيهَا اسْمُهُ يُسَبِّحُ لَهُ فِيهَا بِالْغُدُوِّ وَالْآصَالِ 36 رِجَالٌ لَا تُلْهِيهِمْ تِجَارَةٌ وَلَا بَيْعٌ عَنْ ذِكْرِ اللَّهِ وَإِقَامِ الصَّلَاةِ وَإِيتَاءِ الزَّكَاةِ يَخَافُونَ يَوْمًا تَتَقَلَّبُ فِيهِ الْقُلُوبُ وَالْأَبْصَار</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ُ﴾ [النور: 36-37].</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">قال تعالى: ﴿ {</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #40ad48; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">يَا بَنِي آدَمَ خُذُوا زِينَتَكُمْ عِنْدَ كُلِّ مَسْجِدٍ</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">﴾ [الأعراف:31].</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">عن ابن عمر رضي الله عنهما أن رسول الله [، قال: &laquo;صلاةُ الجماعةِ أفضَلُ من صلاةِ الفَذِّ بسَبعٍ وعشرينَ دَرجةً&raquo; رواه مسلم.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">عن أبي هريرة ] قال: أتى النبي&nbsp; [&nbsp; رَجلٌ أعْمى فقال: يا رسولَ اللهِ، إنَّه ليس لي قائدٌ يَقودُني إلى المسجِدِ، فسألَ رسولَ اللهِ [ أنْ يُرَخِّصَ له فيُصلِّيَ في بيتِه، فرَخَّصَ له، فلمَّا وَلَّى دَعاهُ، فقال: &laquo;هل تَسمَعُ النِّداءَ بالصلاةِ؟&raquo; قال: نَعم، قال: &laquo;فأجِبْ&raquo;. رواه مسلم.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">عن جابر بن عبد الله رضي الله عنهما عن النبي [ قال: &laquo;مَن أكَلَ من هذه البَقْلةِ، الثُّومِ -وقال مرَّةً: مَن أكلَ البصَلَ والثُّومَ والكُرَّاثَ- فلا يَقْرَبَنَّ مسجِدَنا&raquo; رواه مسلم.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>',NULL,'<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">س١/ لماذا نصلي صلاةَ الجماعة ؟</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">س٢/ عَدِّدْ ثلاثة من آداب المسجد.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">س3: </span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">سجل مع زملائك أفكاراً إبداعية للمحافظة على المسجد والاهتمام به.</span></p>\r\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-b48796ab-7fff-587e-2097-9ccf22314429\"></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\">\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>',NULL,49,3,NULL,NULL,'2022-01-13 09:56:58','2022-09-01 11:29:09'),(55,'صلاةُ الجمُعة:','صلاة الجمعة','<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-ba3dd1cb-7fff-c594-90ee-a442f7689521\"></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\">\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; background-color: #e2efd9; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">س/ ما المقصود بصلاة الجمعة&nbsp; وما حكمها؟</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\">\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -54pt;\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; background-color: #e2efd9; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ج/&nbsp; صلاة الجمعة هي: ركعتان، &nbsp; تسبقهما خطبتان،&nbsp; يؤديها المسلمون جماعة،&nbsp; يوم الجمعة، وقت الظهر بدل صلاة الظهر.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; background-color: #e2efd9; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">وتجب على: الرجال البالغين المستوطنين.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; background-color: #e2efd9; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ومن لم يدرك الركعة الثانية من صلاة الجمعة صلى ظهرا أربع ركعات.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>','<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-d48452fd-7fff-fcc5-4e3d-291fd5cefe27\"></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\">\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">قال تعالى: ﴿ يَا أَيُّهَا الَّذِينَ آمَنُوا إِذَا نُودِيَ لِلصَّلَاةِ مِنْ يَوْمِ الْجُمُعَةِ فَاسْعَوْا إِلَى ذِكْرِ اللَّهِ ﴾ [الجمعة: 9].</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: 