-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">الذهب والفضة،</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -54pt;\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; background-color: #e2efd9; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">-والملحق بهما كالأوراق النقدية-،</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -54pt;\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; background-color: #e2efd9; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">وبهيمة الأنعام،</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -54pt;\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; background-color: #e2efd9; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">والحبوب والثمار،</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -54pt;\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; background-color: #e2efd9; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">وعروض التجارة.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-586eb8ac-7fff-c5a7-c530-b20c343e89f1\"></span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; background-color: #e2efd9; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ومن عنده مال منها فعليه تعلم أحكامها.</span></p>','<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-117dd805-7fff-0251-4103-c8842b579fd0\"></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\">\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">قال تعالى: ﴿ وَالَّذِينَ يَكْنِزُونَ الذَّهَبَ وَالْفِضَّةَ وَلَا يُنْفِقُونَهَا فِي سَبِيلِ اللَّهِ فَبَشِّرْهُمْ بِعَذَابٍ أَلِيمٍ﴾ [التوبة: 34].</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">قال تعالى: ﴿ يَا أَيُّهَا الَّذِينَ آمَنُوا أَنْفِقُوا مِنْ طَيِّبَاتِ مَا كَسَبْتُمْ وَمِمَّا أَخْرَجْنَا لَكُمْ مِنَ الْأَرْضِ﴾ [البقرة: 267].</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">عن أبي ذرٍّ ]، عن النبي [؛ أنه قال: &laquo;ما مِن صاحبِ إبلٍ، ولا بقَرٍ، ولا غنَمٍ لا يؤدي زكاتَها: إلا جاءت يوم القيامة أعظَمَ ما كانت، وأسمَنَهُ، تَنطَحُهُ بقرونها، وتطَؤُهُ بأظلافها، كلما نَفِدتْ أُخْراها، عادت عليه أُولاها، حتى يُقضَى بين الناس&raquo;؛ رواه مسلم</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">عن سالم بن عبد الله، عن أبيه، عن النبي [، قال: &laquo;فيما سقَتِ السماءُ والعيونُ، أو كان عَثَريًّا: العُشْرُ، وما سُقِيَ بالنَّضْحِ: نصفُ العُشْرِ&raquo;؛ رواه البخاري. (عَثَريًّا): الذي يشرب بعروقِهِ من ماء المطر.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">عن أبي هُرَيرة ]، عن النبي [ قال: &laquo;وفي الرِّكازِ الخُمُسُ&raquo;؛ متفق عليه</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>',NULL,'<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">س١/ اذكر أمثلةً مما حولك للأموال التي تجب فيها الزكاة، والأموال التي لا تجب فيها الزكاة.</span></p>\r\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-bdeae296-7fff-43f1-b799-fd08a2f84e35\"></span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">س٢/ اذكر بعض فضائل الزكاة؟</span></p>',NULL,NULL,5,NULL,NULL,'2022-01-13 10:03:33','2022-09-01 11:29:09'),(60,'مصارف الزكاة:','مصارف الزكاة','<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-e27bdd57-7fff-65da-d737-567b4d9d5a4e\"></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\">\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; backgr