font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ويكتفى فيها بالإحرام ، والطواف بالبيت، وبين الصفا والمروة، ثم أخذ الشعر.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>','<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-21bc907f-7fff-d841-91b6-1840bd6b6bf4\"></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\">\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">قال تعالى: ﴿</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #40ad48; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> وَأَتِمُّوا الْحَجَّ وَالْعُمْرَةَ لِلَّهِ</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">﴾&nbsp; [البقرة: 196].</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">عن أبي هريرة ] أن رسول الله [ قال: &laquo;العُمْرة إلى العمرة: كفَّارةٌ لِما بينهما، والحجُّ المبرورُ ليس له جزاءٌ إلا الجنَّةُ&raquo; متفق عليه.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,8,NULL,NULL,'2022-01-13 10:19:27','2022-09-01 11:29:09'),(70,'المعامَلات المالية:','المعاملات المالية','<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\">\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; background-color: #e2efd9; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">س/ ما حكم تكسب المال؟&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; background-color: #e2efd9; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ج/ كسبُ المال مباحٌ، لكن:</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; background-color: #e2efd9; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">يحرُمُ كسبُهُ من حرام؛ كالغش، والسرقة، والرشوة،&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; background-color: #e2efd9; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">أو إنفاقه على حرام؛ كالمعاصي،</span></p>\r\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-65a21f4a-7fff-62d8-cae5-597fce512b40\"></span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; background-color: #e2efd9; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">أو الانشغال به عن الواجبات الشرعية، كالصلاة .</span></p>','<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-c17e5fcd-7fff-bf9d-a7c6-88b1b046bbff\"></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\">\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">قال تعالى: ﴿ </span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #40ad48; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">زُيِّنَ لِلنَّاسِ حُبُّ الشَّهَوَاتِ مِنَ النِّسَاء وَالْبَنِينَ وَالْقَنَاطِيرِ الْمُقَنطَرَةِ مِنَ الذَّهَبِ وَالْفِضَّةِ وَالْخَيْلِ الْمُسَوَّمَةِ وَالأَنْعَامِ وَالْحَرْثِ ذَلِكَ مَتَاعُ الْحَيَاةِ الدُّنْيَا وَاللهُ عِندَهُ حُسْنُ الْمَآب</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> ﴾ [آل عمران: 14].</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">قال تعالى: ﴿</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #40ad48; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> الْمَالُ وَالْبَنُونَ زِينَةُ الْحَيَاةِ الدُّنْيَا وَالْبَاقِيَاتُ الصَّالِحَاتُ خَيْرٌ عِنْدَ رَبِّكَ ثَوَابًا وَخَيْرٌ أَمَلًا </span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">﴾ [الكهف: 46].</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">قال تعالى: ﴿ </span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #40ad48; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">إِنَّمَا أَمْوَالُكُمْ وَأَوْلاَدُكُمْ فِتْنَةٌ وَاللَّهُ عِندَهُ أَجْرٌ عَظِيم</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> ﴾ [التغابن: 15].</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">عن كعب بن عِيَاضٍ الأشعَريِّ ]، قال: سمعتُ النبي [ يقول: &laquo;إن لكلِّ أمَّةٍ فتنةً، وفتنة أمَّتي: المالُ&raquo;؛ رواه الترمذي.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">عن أبي هُرَيرة ]، عن النبي [، قال: &laquo;يأتي على الناسِ زمانٌ، لا يبالي المرءُ ما أخَذَ منه، أمِنَ الحلالِ أم من الحرام!&raquo;؛ رواه البخاري.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; colo