background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">وَأَنكِحُوا الأَيَامَى مِنْكُمْ وَالصَّالِحِينَ مِنْ عِبَادِكُمْ وَإِمَائِكُمْ إِنْ يَكُونُوا فُقَرَاءَ يُغْنِهِمُ اللَّهُ مِنْ فَضْلِهِ وَاللَّهُ وَاسِعٌ عَلِيم</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">﴾ [النور:32].</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">قال تعالى: ﴿</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #40ad48; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">وَإِذَا طَلَّقْتُمُ النِّسَاءَ فَبَلَغْنَ أَجَلَهُنَّ فَلا تَعْضُلُوهُنَّ أَنْ يَنْكِحْنَ أَزْوَاجَهُنَّ إِذَا تَرَاضَوْا بَيْنَهُمْ بِالْمَعْرُوفِ</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">﴾ [البقرة 232].</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">عن عبد الله بن مسعود ]، قال: كنا مع النبي [ شبابًا لا نجدُ شيئًا، فقال لنا رسولُ الله صلى الله عليه وسلم: &laquo;يا معشرَ الشباب، مَن استطاع الباءةَ، فليتزوَّجْ؛ فإنه أغَضُّ للبصر، وأحصَنُ للفَرْجِ، ومَن لم يستطع، فعليه بالصوم؛ فإنه له وِجاءٌ&raquo;؛ متفق عليه.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">عن مَعقِلِ بن يسار ]، قال: قال [: &laquo;تزوَّجوا الوَدُودَ الوَلُودَ؛ فإني مكاثِرٌ بكم&raquo;؛ رواه أبو داود.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">عن أبي هُرَيرة ]، قال: قال رسول الله [: &laquo;تُنكَحُ المرأةُ لأربعٍ؛ لمالها، ولحسَبِها، ولجمالها، ولدِينها؛ فاظفَرْ بذات الدِّين تَرِبتْ يداك!&raquo; متفق عليه.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">عن أبي هُرَيرة ]، قال: قال رسول الله [: &laquo;إذا خطَبَ إليكم مَن ترضَوْنَ دِينَهُ وخُلُقه، فزوِّجوه، إلا تفعلوا، تكُنْ فتنةٌ في الأرض، وفسادٌ عريض&raquo;؛ رواه الترمذي وغيره.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>',NULL,'<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\">\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #d37695; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">س١/</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #9f8f8a; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ما الحكمة من مشروعية النكاح؟</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #d37695; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">س٢/</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #9f8f8a; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ما حكم النكاح؟</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #d37695; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">س٣/</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #9f8f8a; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ما الصفات التي تطلب في الرجل والمرأة عند النكاح؟</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-1da54ff8-7fff-2425-ff1a-5d65899d3824\">&nbsp;</span></p>',NULL,73,9,NULL,NULL,'2022-01-13 10:25:47','2022-09-01 11:29:09'),(75,'معنى الزكاة، وحُكْمُها:','معنى الزكاة، وحكمها',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,5,NULL,'2022-01-13 10:30:37','2022-01-13 10:30:37','2022-09-01 11:29:09'),(76,'المحرَّمات في النكاح:','المحرمات في النكاح','<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; background-color: #e2efd9; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">س/ من اللائي يحرُمُ الزواج بهن؟</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; background-color: #e2efd9; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ج/ يحرُمُ زواج الرجُلِ: بأمهاته ،</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; background-color: #e2efd9; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">وبناته،</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; background-color: #e2efd9; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">وأخواته،</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; background-color: #e2efd9; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">وعماته، وخالاته، وبنات أخيه، وبنات أخته،</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; background-color: #e2efd9; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">وأمهات زوجاته، وزوجات أبنائه.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; background-color: #e2efd9; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ويدخل في جميع ما سبق ما علت أو نزلت درجتهن، وما كان شقيقا أو لأب أو لأم،</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; background-color: #e2efd9; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">وما كان من النسب أو من الرضاعة.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; background-color: #e2efd9; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ولا يجمع بين المرأة وأختها، أو خالتها، أو عمتها.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; background-color: #e2efd9; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ولا يتزوج المرأةَ وهي متزوجة، أو مطلَّقة لم تُتِمَّ عِدَّتها.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; background-color: #e2efd9; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ولا يتزوج بأكثرَ من أربع.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; background-color: #e2efd9; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ولا تتزوَّجُ المرأةُ بغير مسلم.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; background-color: #e2efd9; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ولا يتزوج الرجُلُ بغير مسلمة، أو يهودية، أو نصرانية.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; background-color: #e2efd9; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ولا يكون الزواج بزانٍ أو زانية لم يتوبا، أو بمن يكون سببا للضلالة في الدين.</span></p>\r\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-f2f9fb07-7fff-6f55-0542-deda9e2291c0\"></span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; background-color: #e2efd9; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ولا يتزوج بدون رضا الطرفين، ولا بدون مهر وولي وشاهدين</span></p>','<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-5f13121e-7fff-acb7-fc39-c32495b9b119\"></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\">\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">قال تعالى: ﴿ حُرِّمَتْ عَلَيْكُمْ أُمَّهَاتُكُمْ وَبَنَاتُكُمْ وَأَخَوَاتُكُمْ وَعَمَّاتُكُمْ وَخَالَاتُكُمْ وَبَنَاتُ الْأَخِ وَبَنَاتُ الْأُخْتِ وَأُمَّهَاتُكُمُ اللَّاتِي أَرْضَعْنَكُمْ وَأَخَوَاتُكُمْ مِنَ الرَّضَاعَةِ وَأُمَّهَاتُ نِسَائِكُمْ وَرَبَائِبُكُمُ اللَّاتِي فِي حُجُورِكُمْ مِنْ نِسَائِكُمُ اللَّاتِي دَخَلْتُمْ بِهِنَّ فَإِنْ لَمْ تَكُونُوا دَخَلْتُمْ بِهِنَّ فَلَا جُنَاحَ عَلَيْكُمْ وَحَلَائِلُ أَبْنَائِكُمُ الَّذِينَ مِنْ أَصْلَابِكُمْ وَأَنْ تَجْمَعُوا بَيْنَ الْأُخْتَيْنِ إِلَّا مَا قَدْ سَلَفَ إِنَّ اللَّهَ كَانَ غَفُورًا رَحِيمًا ﴾ [النساء: 23].</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">قال تعالى: ﴿ فَانْكِحُوا مَا طَابَ لَكُمْ مِنَ النِّسَاءِ مَثْنَى وَثُلَاثَ وَرُبَاعَ فَإِنْ خِفْتُمْ أَلَّا تَعْدِلُوا فَوَاحِدَةً أَوْ مَا مَلَكَتْ أَيْمَانُكُمْ﴾ [النساء: 3].</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">قال تعالى: ﴿ وَلَا تَنْكِحُوا الْمُشْرِكَاتِ حَتَّى يُؤْمِنَّ وَلَأَمَةٌ مُؤْمِنَةٌ خَيْرٌ مِنْ مُشْرِكَةٍ وَلَوْ أَعْجَبَتْكُمْ وَلَا تُنْكِحُوا الْمُشْرِكِينَ حَتَّى يُؤْمِنُوا وَلَعَبْدٌ مُؤْمِنٌ خَيْرٌ مِنْ مُشْرِكٍ وَلَوْ أَعْجَبَكُمْ أُولَئِكَ يَدْعُونَ إِلَى النَّارِ ﴾ [البقرة: 221].</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">عن ابن عباس رضي الله عنهما عن النبي&nbsp; [ قال: &laquo;لا نكاحَ إلا بوليٍّ، وشاهدَيْ عدلٍ&raquo; رواه البيهقي.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;عن أبي هريرة ] أن النبي&nbsp; [&nbsp; قال: &laquo;لا تُنكَحُ الأيِّمُ حتى تُستأمر، ولا تُنكَح البِكْرُ حتى تُستأذن&raquo;، قالوا: يا رسول الله، وكيف إذنُها؟ قال: &laquo;أن تسكُتَ&raquo; متفق عليه.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>',NULL,'<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\">\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">س١/ مَن هن المحرَّمات في النكاح بسبب النسب والقرابة؟</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">س٢/ مَن هن المحرَّمات في النكاح بسبب المصاهرة؟</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #ff0000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: right; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">س٣/ ما حكم زواج رجل وامرأة؛ يتفقان ويذهبان للقاضي؟</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-86230669-7fff-ce84-d424-6f33fa00bea5\">&nbsp;</span></p>',NULL,73,9,NULL,NULL,'2022-01-13 10:37:10','2022-09-01 11:29:09'),(77,'الحقوق والواجبات بين الزوجين:','الحقوق والواجبات بين الزوجين','<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-94adc9dd-7fff-b575-2196-a13f5c8400be\"></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\">\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; background-color: #e2efd9; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">س/ ماذا يَلزَم كلًّا من الزوجينِ للآخر؟</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; background-color: #e2efd9; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ج/ تلزم العِشْرةُ بالحسنى، كما يعرفه عقلاء الناس، بحسب عادات كل بلد، ما لم يكن حراما أو مضرته راجحة.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; background-color: #e2efd9; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">وعلى الزوج: النفقةُ المعتادة لمثل حالهما.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-styl