 baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ج/ تؤخذ الشريعةُ عن الله تعالى من القرآن الكريم، وعن رسوله [ من السُّنة النبوية.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; background-color: #e2efd9; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ويدخل فيهما: إذا دل إجماع علماء المسلمين على حكم مسألة.</span></p>\r\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-34c51579-7fff-07fa-fffc-0b451efb8ba0\"></span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; background-color: #e2efd9; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">وإذا كانت هناك مسألة لم تذكر فيهما: فيعرف حكمها بالقياس الصحيح على أقرب حكم مذكور فيهما .</span></p>','<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-b74af5fb-7fff-51bc-f7e8-3c081723d292\"></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\">\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">قال تعالى: ﴿ </span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #40ad48; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">وَنَزَّلْنَا عَلَيْكَ الْكِتَابَ تِبْيَانًا لِكُلِّ شَيْءٍ</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">﴾ [النحل: 86].</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">قال تعالى: ﴿ </span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #40ad48; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">قُلْ أَطِيعُوا اللهَ وَالرَّسُولَ</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> ﴾ [آل عمران: 32].</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">قال تعالى: ﴿</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #40ad48; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> وَمَا آتَاكُمُ الرَّسُولُ فَخُذُوهُ وَمَا نَهَاكُمْ عَنْهُ فَانْتَهُوا</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">﴾ [الحشر: 7].</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">قال تعالى: ﴿ </span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #40ad48; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">وَمَن يُشَاقِقِ الرَّسُولَ مِن بَعْدِ مَا تَبَيَّنَ لَهُ الْهُدَى وَيَتَّبِعْ غَيْرَ سَبِيلِ الْمُؤْمِنِينَ نُوَلِّهِ مَا تَوَلَّى وَنُصْلِهِ جَهَنَّمَ وَسَاءتْ مَصِيرًا</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">﴾ [النساء:115].&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">عن المِقْدام بن معدي كَرِبَ ]، عن رسول الله [؛ أنه قال: &laquo;ألَا إني أوتِيتُ الكتابَ ومِثلَهُ معه&raquo;؛ رواه أبو داود.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">عن العِرْباض بن ساريةَ ]؛ أن رسول الله [ وعَظَهم ذات يوم، فقال: &laquo;فعليكم بسُنَّتي، وسُنَّة الخلفاء المَهْديين الراشدين؛ تمسَّكوا بها، وعَضُّوا عليها بالنواجذ&raquo;؛ رواه أبو داود.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">عن ابن عمرَ رضي الله عنهما؛ أن رسولَ الله [ قال: &laquo;إن اللهَ لا يَجمَعُ أمَّتي - أو قال: أمَّةَ محمد [ - على ضلالةٍ&raquo;؛ رواه الترمذي.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>',NULL,'<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-2165567c-7fff-a71c-b225-c7a09fdf4559\"></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\">\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #ac897c; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">س1/</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #9f8f8a; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">هناك مصدران أساسيان تؤخذ منهما الأحكام الإسلامية؛ فما هما؟</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #ac897c; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #ac897c; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">س2/ صمم خريطة مفاهيم للقرآن والسُّنة، وتحتهما الإجماع والقياس، مع ذكر مثال لحُكْمٍ مأخوذ من كل واحد منها.&emsp;</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>',NULL,NULL,11,NULL,NULL,'2022-01-13 11:31:17','2022-09-01 11:29:09'),(94,'كيفية معرفة الحُكْمِ الشرعي:','كيفية معرفة الحكم الشرعي','<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-b6abe602-7fff-24d7-409e-d6d6ec100bbf\"></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\">\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; background-color: #e2efd9; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">س/ كيف نَعرِفُ الحُكْمَ الشرعي لمسألة؟</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; background-color: #e2efd9; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ج/ من لم يَعلَمِ الحكم الشرعي من القرآن والسُّنَّة، سأل أهل العلم بهما.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\">\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">قال تعالى:&nbsp; ﴿</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #40ad48; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> فَاسْأَلُوا أَهْلَ الذِّكْرِ إِنْ كُنْتُمْ لا تَعْلَمُونَ</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">﴾ [النحل: 43].</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">قال تعالى: ﴿</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #40ad48; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> يَرْفَعِ اللَّهُ الَّذِينَ آمَنُوا مِنْكُمْ وَالَّذِينَ أُوتُوا الْعِلْمَ دَرَجَاتٍ</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">﴾ [المجادلة: 11].</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">قال تعالى: ﴿</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #40ad48; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> وَقُلْ رَبِّ زِدْنِي عِلْمًا</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">﴾ [طه: 114].</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">قال تعالى: ﴿</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">وَلَوْ عَلِمَ اللَّهُ فِيهِمْ خَيْرًا لأَسْمَعَهُمْ وَلَوْ أَسْمَعَهُمْ لَتَوَلَّوْا وَهُمْ مُعْرِضُونَ﴾ [الأنفال: 23].</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">عن أنس بن مالك ]، قال: قال رسول الله [: &laquo;طلبُ العلم فريضةٌ على كل مسلمٍ&raquo;؛ رواه ابن ماجه.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">عن جابر ]، قال: خرَجْنا في سفَرٍ، فأصاب رجُلًا منا حجَرٌ، فشجَّهُ في رأسه، ثم احتلم، فسأل أصحابه، فقال: هل تجدون لي رخصةً في التيمُّم؟ فقالوا: ما نجد لك رخصةً وأنت تَقدِرُ على الماء؛ فاغتسل، فمات، فلما قَدِمْنا على النبي [، أُخبِرَ بذلك، فقال: &laquo;قتَلوه، قتَلهم اللهُ، ألا سألوا إذ لم يَعلَموا؛ فإنما شفاءُ العِيِّ: السؤالُ&raquo;؛ رواه أبو داود.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: -18pt;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"rtl\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">عن عبد الله بن عمرو بن العاص رضي الله عنهما، قال: سمعتُ رسول الله [ يقول: &laquo;إن اللهَ لا يَقبِضُ العلمَ انتزاعًا ينتزعُهُ من العباد، ولكن يَقبِضُ العلمَ بقَبْضِ العلماء، حتى إذا لم يُبقِ عالِمًا، اتخذ الناسُ رؤوسًا جهالًا، فسُئِلوا، فأفتَوْا بغير علم؛ فضَلُّوا وأضَلُّوا&raquo;؛ رواه البخاري.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"rtl\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Traditional Arabic\'; color: #3c3c3e; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;